Package com.java.BankingSystem

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    Basic account class to be extended by specialised accounts.
    BalanceDisplayer
    Displays a users balance to them.
    BankConsole
    BankConsole is the class a user will interact with, this creates and calls all accounts, customers and their respective methods.
    CurrentAccount
    Current Account extends Account to inherit its properties while implementing new methods of its own.
    Customer
    Customer is the class used to create each customer and collect their information.
    IsaAccount
    IsaAccount inherits from account to create an account specialised to handle the logic of an ISA Account.
